%div.site-wrapper

  :javascript
    new WOW({mobile: false}).init();


  %div.site-wrapper-inner
    

    %div.cover-container

      .container
        %button.navbar-toggle{"data-target" => ".navbar-collapse", "data-toggle" => "collapse", :type => "button"}
          %span.sr-only Toggle navigation
          %span.icon-bar
          %span.icon-bar
          %span.icon-bar
        = link_to image_tag('dg_logo.png', :class => 'logo'), root_path, :class => 'navbar-brand'
        
        .collapse.navbar-collapse
          %ul.nav.navbar-nav.navbar-right  
            %li 
              = link_to 'Sign in', "#sign-in", :class => 'btn btn-lg sign-in btn-warning pull-right navbar-btn', "data-toggle" => "modal"
            %li 
              = link_to 'Contact', contact_path, :class => 'pull-right navbar-btn contact'
      %div.inner.cover.center.container
        = render 'layouts/messages'
        
        .animated.fadeInUp
          %h1.cover-heading.space 
            Welcome to 
            %span CrushTopia. 
          %h3.white A land of magic and great software!
          
          %i.scroll.fa.fa-chevron-down{'href' => '#first'}
        
        %p.lead 
          
    
        
    %div.col-md-12.fp-ht.fp-first.fp-long
      .container.icons-top.center
        .col-md-4
          %i.fa.fa-compass
          %h3 Strategic.
          %p We think on a system-level to make sure we create the most leverage with our products.
        .col-md-4
          %i.fa.fa-graduation-cap
          %h3 Intelligent.
          %p We simply hire the best minds in the business. 
        .col-md-4
          %i.fa.fa-connectdevelop
          %h3 Connected.
          %p We play in the internet of things. Ask us about our thoughts on deployed sensors sometime.

        .col-md-12.fp-title
          %h1 So, why work with us?
    
    %div.slide-one.col-lg-12.fp-ht.wow.slideInLeft{"data-wow-delay" =>"0.15s"}
      .container
        .row
          .col-md-3.col-md-offset-1.mob-center
            %i.thumb.fa.fa-thumbs-o-up
          .col-md-8
            %h3.pink Doing business with us is easy.​​
            %p We are a force multiplier for your business goals. We bring you effective, efficient processes throughout development with no red tape or wasted time.

    %div.col-md-12.fp-ht
      .container.pull-right.wow.slideInRight{"data-wow-delay" =>"0.15s"}
        .row
          .col-sm-3.col-md-offset-1.col-sm-push-7.mob-center
            %i.rocket.fa.fa-rocket
          .col-sm-7.col-sm-pull-3
            %h3.purple Iterative development from concept to deployment.​
            %p  We’re builders and problem solvers at heart with a bias towards action. We strive to get a working prototype into your hands fast​, that allows you to implement, iterate, and re­deploy better and better products.
          

    %div.col-md-12.fp-ht.wow.slideInLeft{"data-wow-delay" =>"0.15s"}
      .container
        .row
          .col-md-3.col-md-offset-1.mob-center
            %i.cogs.fa.fa-cogs
          .col-md-7
            %h3.pink We know business, technology, and product development.​
            %p The talent across our team is immense. Our development services range from technology consulting and business analysis to QA, application maintenance and solution integration. We have full­stack capabilities.
    %div.col-md-12.fp-ht.wow.slideInRight
      .container.pull-right
        .row
          .col-sm-3.col-md-offset-1.col-sm-push-7.mob-center
            %i.signs.fa.fa-map-signs
          .col-sm-7.col-sm-pull-3
            %h3.purple We provide scalable, future­proof products.​
            %p We pair agile development with scalable technology, so that when you’re successful, your software adapts. We architect systems that work now and in the future.
          
